{"tid":2273241,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共最叻就係喺真新聞入面加插啲假嘢，等人之後連啲真嘢都質疑","createTime":"2020-11-05T14:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:59:23.000Z","uid":44209,"like":577,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"aae990851c83d4f757a3ea04636cafde15ee8a32","tid":2273241,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"古有法輪功大紀元，活摘器官我信係有發生過，不過中共當中可能加插啲假case，又或者喺啲枝節上面改下，然後扮踢爆澄清，之後話活摘器官都冇發生過<br />\n<br />\n到依家都冇乜人信大紀元嘅報道，又覺得法輪功係玩膠（明明佢哋係反共始祖嚟）。無可否認大紀元有啲報道可能誇張咗少少，但未至於完全信唔過<br />\n<br />\n講返香港，浮屍丶狗屋入面打人丶強姦示威者，呢啲一定有發生過，但中共又係用同一種手法，嘗試去令到我哋誠信減低（呢度手法可能有少少唔同，例如未必每單命案、自殺都關手足事，但總有人走出嚟「<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，可能之後會有人因為咁而問「係咪真係咁黑警棄屍啊」<br />\n<br />\n去到美國大選，民主黨造票，丟trump嘅票，我相信都一定有發生，中共/民主黨就放啲fake news出嚟，再去澄清話冇咁嘅事，手法同搞9法輪功嗰事一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n所以有時間可以先search一下係咪fake news/ old news，廢事炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bda9c7f4943414a7c7f36a75d042ec71aa8f55f","tid":2273241,"uid":155095,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/17823/a1-1@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F17823%2Fa1-1%401200x1200.jpg&h=e812e178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2018/0717/20180717072652802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2018%2F0717%2F20180717072652802.jpg&h=869f0be2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4107efe171f55f90be566d71720996f5ac7cc875","tid":2273241,"uid":92859,"like":201,"dislike":2,"score":199,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"以前有「返工不了」<br />\n依加有「手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n咁明顯嘅PR手法點解仲會有啲on9仔跟風"},{"pid":"4dc2734cb84f9c52e563d7f76663cc76c8c61609","tid":2273241,"uid":3177,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"你反既 人地滲入埋你度 講你講既說話 講得大聲過你 再反cup 死得"},{"pid":"4ed503e99119822cfc29c2784d013968b1079125","tid":2273241,"uid":44209,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"即刻有一個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國郵遞選票預先填寫biden<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2273232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2273232</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"daa578cdbc72174b49c3e9a8813505b86d6ee72c","tid":2273241,"uid":50386,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"香港狗隊都係咁玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a430bce48f2053a0ce6b4e8b223996d6a796ea","tid":2273241,"uid":46947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"最正就係播嚟播去都係嗰啲片，<br />\n最啱呃廢老用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fdae2cbbd03cd31e0958a658d24b987c3a416e","tid":2273241,"uid":252854,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"真 同埋見到啲所謂Fact check網好多時話部分真實 部分唔真實咁想去discredit成件事"},{"pid":"f5c34b6e3bbb1ff34784b340239459a26ada5cc7","tid":2273241,"uid":241628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e32cfcd204695b7f00160fe8adaa68f36cd4b4b4","tid":2273241,"uid":269202,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"用左膠既邏輯去諗下，其實有冇證據都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界唔存在一種佢地相信既證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我信毆打，骨折，斷手斷腳，水刑，同埋手淫"},{"pid":"78b7d27f94527d5627cf7bdeb0639c504309d549","tid":2273241,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ff2d00